  <name>Bildstöd</name>
  <summary>ARASAAC pictogram search and visual communication tool</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Bildstöd helps create visual communication boards using ARASAAC pictograms.
      Search over 13,000 free pictograms, create picture schedules, and export
      boards for printing. Designed for children and adults who use AAC
      (Augmentative and Alternative Communication).
    </p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Search 13,000+ ARASAAC pictograms</li>
      <li>Create visual communication boards</li>
      <li>Drag and drop pictograms</li>
      <li>Export boards as images or PDF</li>
      <li>Dark/light theme support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
